msgid "Fluid and participative online dialogues"
msgstr ""

#, safe-html
msgctxt "description1"
msgid ""
"Stooa is an online platform that allows fluid and participatory "
"conversations for large groups and with automatic facilitation <span>based "
"on the fishbowl method.</span>"
msgstr ""

#, safe-html
msgctxt "description2"
msgid ""
"It is an <span>ideal dialogue method</span> for communities, educational "
"environments, or companies that seek to improve the experience of their "
"employees."
