#, safe-html
msgctxt "definition.title"
msgid "What is the fishbowl method?"
msgstr ""

#, safe-html
msgctxt "definition.description"
msgid ""
"<p>A fishbowl is a <strong>group dynamic</strong> that facilitates "
"conversations, debates and any type of activity in which "
"<strong>participation is essential for its development</strong>.</p><p>It is "
"an ideal dialogue method for communities, educational environments, or "
"companies looking to improve their employee experience.</p>"
msgstr ""

#, safe-html
msgctxt "howOnlineDebates"
msgid ""
"How do we achieve smooth and participative online discussions with large "
"groups?"
msgstr ""

#, safe-html
msgctxt "howStooa.title"
msgid "How does Stooa work?"
msgstr ""

#, safe-html
msgctxt "howStooa.subtitle"
msgid "It's very simple!"
msgstr ""

#, safe-html
msgctxt "howStooa.firstBulletTitle"
msgid "5 seats to dialogue"
msgstr ""

#, safe-html
msgctxt "howStooa.firstBulletSub"
msgid ""
"To participate in the dialogue you will have to occupy one of the available "
"seats."
msgstr ""

#, safe-html
msgctxt "howStooa.secondBulletTitle"
msgid "1 Free seat to encourage participation"
msgstr ""

#, safe-html
msgctxt "howStooa.secondBulletSub"
msgid "There must always be a free seat."
msgstr ""

#, safe-html
msgctxt "howStooa.longExplanation1"
msgid ""
"Any attendee can <span>occupy a free chair</span> at any time <span>to "
"participate in the dialogue</span>."
msgstr ""

#, safe-html
msgctxt "howStooa.longExplanation2"
msgid ""
"If all <span>chairs are occupied</span> someone who has already participated "
"must <span>leave their seat</span>."
msgstr ""

#, safe-html
msgctxt "keybenefits.first.title"
msgid "More participation"
msgstr ""

#, safe-html
msgctxt "keybenefits.first.description"
msgid ""
"All participants feel engaged, maintain attention, and can move in and out "
"of the fishbowl as they wish to enter the conversation. The hierarchy is "
"removed and the level of engagement of the participants increases."
msgstr ""

#, safe-html
msgctxt "keybenefits.second.title"
msgid "Fluency & automatic facilitation"
msgstr ""

#, safe-html
msgctxt "keybenefits.second.description"
msgid ""
"The conversation between the attendees occurs spontaneously without the need "
"for a moderator. The tool adapts to the method and guides the user, "
"indicating the times and the steps to follow."
msgstr ""

#, safe-html
msgctxt "keybenefits.third.title"
msgid "Shared knowledge"
msgstr ""

#, safe-html
msgctxt "keybenefits.third.description"
msgid ""
"Participants' opinions emerge as the conversation progresses, and the topics "
"of greatest interest are explored in depth from different points of view."
msgstr ""

#, safe-html
msgctxt "keybenefits.fourth.title"
msgid "Informal connections"
msgstr ""

#, safe-html
msgctxt "keybenefits.fourth.description"
msgid ""
"Attendees can share experiences, meet the rest of the participants and build "
"their own network of informal or professional contacts."
msgstr ""

#, safe-html
msgctxt "banner"
msgid ""
"Create your free fishbowl activity and invite participants. Let the "
"conversation begin!"
msgstr ""
